She looked down to see Ursa Major's lifeless body laying there.  She looked 
to see Double Punch pointing his weapon at her at point blank range.  She 
whispered, "Why do you want me dead so badly?  What have I done to you?"  
She had trouble breathing and her body shook from the pain.  "Why?"  was all 
she could find the strength to say.
